,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:09:38.000Z","msg":"之後個幾場點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24bee2a57801404e9f15a1edbdb1ceec96fb37f","tid":974184,"uid":64075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"呢個咩app黎傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"87d7835b0757ae8808393380838afc87d7a7a18e","tid":974184,"uid":209786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b24bee2a57801404e9f15a1edbdb1ceec96fb37f","tid":974184,"uid":64075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"呢個咩app黎傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:22:02.000Z","msg":"同問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698ea0823a58145fe9142bb3937fe2eaa8e5289c","tid":974184,"uid":15407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:32:42.000Z","msg":"強"},{"pid":"bb62da23aa3a03c07077b259883402e082e91401","tid":974184,"uid":177060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b24bee2a57801404e9f15a1edbdb1ceec96fb37f","tid":974184,"uid":64075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"呢個咩app黎傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:34:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vip.bfindex.com/sc/news_popup.php?newsID=2593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvip.bfindex.com%2Fsc%2Fnews_popup.php%3FnewsID%3D2593&d=RVE7oYzF4ieQY3de9c1%2B%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bc60e8e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://vip.bfindex.com/sc/news_popup.php?newsID=2593</a><br />\n必發指數網<br />\nfacebook有d賣賭波料既都係用呢個app，話係參考大陸佬落盤而分析出黎既。我就咁睇左一陣間，發覺佢盤的來源都只係佢自己本身交易所，而分析唔到其他地方的盤源，例如馬會,威廉希爾。所以要人地瀉盤先可以準確反映市場真正走勢，我無畀錢但估計佢地未有咁勁。<br />\n<br />\n至於佢個d所謂技術分析，改一改graph睇法其實真係同股票分析有d相似，係咪堅就見人見智，未研究過唔敢否定呢樣野，大家繼續討論。"},{"pid":"5754dc199dd7dd3f465f91a266fc0ee0ceb93e18","tid":974184,"uid":177060,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"bb62da23aa3a03c07077b259883402e082e91401","tid":974184,"uid":177060,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"b24bee2a57801404e9f15a1edbdb1ceec96fb37f","tid":974184,"uid":64075,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:21:15.000Z","msg":"呢個咩app黎傢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:34:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://vip.bfindex.com/sc/news_popup.php?newsID=2593\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvip.bfindex.com%2Fsc%2Fnews_popup.php%3FnewsID%3D2593&d=RVE7oYzF4ieQY3de9c1%2B%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=bc60e8e6\" target=\"_blank\">https://vip.bfindex.com/sc/news_popup.php?newsID=2593</a><br />\n必發指數網<br />\nfacebook有d賣賭波料既都係用呢個app，話係參考大陸佬落盤而分析出黎既。我就咁睇左一陣間，發覺佢盤的來源都只係佢自己本身交易所，而分析唔到其他地方的盤源，例如馬會,威廉希爾。所以要人地瀉盤先可以準確反映市場真正走勢，我無畀錢但估計佢地未有咁勁。<br />\n<br />\n至於佢個d所謂技術分析，改一改graph睇法其實真係同股票分析有d相似，係咪堅就見人見智，未研究過唔敢否定呢樣野，大家繼續討論。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T20:38:50.000Z","msg":"我唔係樓主，只係用佢張圖睇下料望下，睇下有咩可以參考：<br />\nQUANTITATIVE ANALYSIS<br />\nQuantitative analysis are also known as quants. This approach uses mathematical principles of specialised database analysis. Yes, it sounds kind of complicated and to be honest it is.<br />\n<br />\nPeople who work on identifying this kind of bet will usually have a deep knowledge of maths. It isn&rsquo;t the sort of thing that anyone can just dive in and get started on. You can&rsquo;t expect to just start doing this well from the start.<br />\n<br />\nRather, it is more likely that you rely upon an expert to do this for you. Value betting services will identify the bets that they think you should make. Some will use this approach to do so.<br />\n<br />\nOf course, if you are a number cruncher extraordinaire you might use this way of identifying value bets. It is an incredibly satisfying way of identifying bets if you have the skills needed to do it.<br />\n<img src=\"https://mikecruickshank.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/Quants-1024x690.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmikecruickshank.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2FQuants-1024x690.png&h=bb4b6e0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://mikecruickshank.com/value-betting/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmikecruickshank.com%2Fvalue-betting%2F&d=RVE7oYzF4ieQY3de9c1%2B%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=1d9e9b9c\" target=\"_blank\">https://mikecruickshank.com/value-betting/</a>"},{"pid":"5f26d20cbebde1fbd188f1f6d3727112e0fcab35","tid":974184,"uid":177060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T22:01:06.000Z","msg":"大交易，賠率升：應該買<br />\n大交易，賠率跌：唔應該買<br />\n其他幾個頂，上升下降軌就股票都用到<br />\n初哥9up，訓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a37afece16fa617be6ba6ab84f4104812b8f45b","tid":974184,"uid":177060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-08T22:02:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大交易，賠率<span style=\"color: red;\">跌</span>：應該買<br />\n大交易，賠率<span style=\"color: red;\">升</span>：唔應該買<br />\n其他幾個頂，上升下降軌就股票都用到<br />\n初哥9up，訓了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好眼訓打錯字sorry<br />\n<a href=\"https://vip.bfindex.com/sc/news_popup.php?newsID=2596\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvip.bfindex.com%2Fsc%2Fnews_popup.php%3FnewsID%3D2596&d=RVE7oYzF4ieQY3de9c1%2B%2FghMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=63cb717a\" target=\"_blank\">https://vip.bfindex.com/sc/news_popup.php?newsID=2596</a><br />\n不過熱刺個場大交易，賠率升都照贏"},{"pid":"08f11cfab6a2cf4105aabecbe6e12c08139e9b8c","tid":974184,"uid":145712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T10:55:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HkxAb7u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHkxAb7u.jpg&h=8016ef65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n2.5s 有大注